---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center h-full">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-nvim-blue">About</h1>
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="mb-4">version 0.0.1</p>
      <div class="flex flex-col text-left justify-left p-10">
        <p class="p-4">
          Welcome to <a class="font-bold text-nvim-blue">HORIZON</a>, A
          community created by <a class="font-bold text-nvim-blue">nerds</a> for <a
            class="font-bold text-nvim-blue">nerds</a
          >
          inspired by the legendary <a class="font-bold text-nvim-blue">Vim</a> console.
          Yet the initial creator himself doesn't understand vim properly. The idea
          behind this website is to create a place for us to share our knowledge and
          experiences with each other.
        </p>
        <p class="p-4">
          Our landing page harnesses the power of Vim’s efficient and minimalist
          design, bringing the speed and functionality of the console to the
          web. With support for key bindings, you can navigate and interact with
          the page just as you would in your favorite editor.
        </p>
        <p class="p-4">
          <a class="font-bold italic">Why Vim?</a>
          Vim is renowned for its unparalleled efficiency and control, allowing developers
          to perform complex text manipulations with just a few keystrokes. It's a
          tool that, once mastered, transforms the coding experience, making it faster
          and more enjoyable.
        </p>
        <p class="p-4">
          Join us on this journey to redefine open knowledge sharing. Embrace
          the philosophy of collaborative growth and see how it revolutionizes
          the way we build and shape our community. Welcome to a new era where
          technical mastery meets open collaboration—this is HORIZON.
        </p>
        <p class="p-4">
          Whether you're here to learn, to teach, or simply to explore the
          efficiency of a Vim-inspired web, there's a place for you in our
          community. Let's build something better, together.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
